      <title>Advent 与 Duke’s Mayo 所有者 Sauer Brands 达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/advent-reaches-deal-for-duke-s-mayo-owner-sauer-brands</link>
