    <item>
      <title>美联储库克称官员们在降息方面可以更加谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/fed-s-cook-says-officials-can-be-more-cautious-with-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事丽莎·库克表示，由于劳动力市场强劲且通胀压力持续存在，政策制定者可以更加谨慎地采取降息措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/fed-s-cook-says-officials-can-be-more-cautious-with-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 14:10:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>因担心科特迪瓦出口放缓将导致供应紧张，可可价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/cocoa-gains-on-fears-slowing-ivorian-exports-will-tighten-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们越来越担心主要生产国科特迪瓦的供应减少将进一步挤压本已紧张的市场，纽约可可价格创下一周多以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/cocoa-gains-on-fears-slowing-ivorian-exports-will-tighten-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 13:45:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纯果乐供应商因疾病和风暴停止柑橘生产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/tropicana-supplier-alico-to-shut-citrus-unit-as-industry-suffers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alico 公司是美国最大的柑橘种植商之一，也是 Tropicana 的供应商。由于病害和飓风导致其柑橘产量连续数十年下降，该公司将关闭其柑橘部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/tropicana-supplier-alico-to-shut-citrus-unit-as-industry-suffers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 13:32:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普否认削减关税报告后美元缩减跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/dollar-falls-most-in-two-months-on-report-trump-to-limit-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普否认有关他的关税计划不会像最初担心的那样广泛的报道后，美元兑大多数主要货币周一大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/dollar-falls-most-in-two-months-on-report-trump-to-limit-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 12:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
